Package com.binance4j.websocket.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WebsocketEventHandler  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseWebsocketEventHandler
    The base class of every WebsocketEventHandler
    WebsocketCloseClientHandler
    Will close the client after WebsocketClientConfiguration.closeAfter
    WebsocketConnectionHandler
    Reconnects or disconnects the client according to WebsocketClientConfiguration.getReconnectionInterval() and WebsocketClientConfiguration.getMaxReconnections()
    WebsocketDisconnectionHandler
    Forces the closing of the client if it is stuck on closing state
    WebsocketForceClosingHandler
    Forces the call of the onClosing and onClosed event handlers of the WebsocketClient's WebsocketInterceptorCallback
    WebsocketNoResponseHandler
    Disconnects the client if no data was received in the interval defined by WebsocketClientConfiguration.getNoResponseTimeout()
